{"tid":1200499,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[強積金終於有用]將香港股票基金轉做外國股票基金票","createTime":"2019-06-10T18:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T19:02:14.000Z","uid":258381,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"182e6154b1101855b0bd22f7177ef03ece526a1c","tid":1200499,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:18:46.000Z","msg":"當有人提出將港幣兌美金可以影響港匯，而大家擔心無錢做呢件事<br />\n大家係咪遺忘左自己一直有份唔細不過無用既資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錯，就係個份強姦金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（本人做banking絕對知佢幾廢）<br />\n<br />\n在2018年9月30日，強積金總資產值達$8,583億<br />\n（ <a href=\"http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/information_centre/press_releases/8210_record.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfa.org.hk%2Ftch%2Finformation_centre%2Fpress_releases%2F8210_record.jsp&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lYmB5A%2F6U2CfHiGB6dLXW7A%3D&h=0da38354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/information_centre/press_releases/8210_record.jsp</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n截至2019年5月31日<br />\n- 混合資產基金   209<br />\n- 股票基金   162<br />\n- 債券基金   43<br />\n- 貨幣市場基金 - 強積金保守基金   32<br />\n- 保證基金   21<br />\n- 貨幣市場基金 - 不包括強積金保守基金   9<br />\n( <a href=\"http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/information_centre/statistics/mpf_statistics_update/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfa.org.hk%2Ftch%2Finformation_centre%2Fstatistics%2Fmpf_statistics_update%2Findex.jsp&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lYmB5A%2F6U2CfHiGB6dLXW7A%3D&h=a89d7f02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/information_centre/statistics/mpf_statistics_update/index.jsp</a> )<br />\n<br />\n近年大家不斷吹捧股票基金，相信香港都有2-4成（有無專家有數據？）MPF係以港幣計價投資香港資產<br />\n假如呢d香港股票強姦金有1/3轉做外國資產，保守估計都有8583 * 20% * 1/3 = HKD572億流出香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且轉MPF對一般人黎講基本上係零影響（因為本來都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n所以大家不妨定期更新強積金投資組合<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：本人做左幾年CD-ROM，今日都比政府逼左出黎，開個ac做連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為一個成日坐而體弱既banker，勇武就未必得架喇<br />\n既然今晚要等sign-off，不如就分享下財技<br />\n<br />\n近半年做埋DCM野，成日見大陸公司用低yield發債refinancing，其實都諗到其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時間係Bloomberg search夠料再分享下"},{"pid":"1bc18e3bd859f84877d24e6c64a82aa4b341d74b","tid":1200499,"uid":138233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67348e07e412a9b3e3e2d78bf78df2cc5f89a73","tid":1200499,"uid":138233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceaad5af8324ca3b10ae062283a12e0377321258","tid":1200499,"uid":215634,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:43:21.000Z","msg":"多得大家一齊諗偈，呢招好似真係"},{"pid":"d6ee71108a6bda093aa2cff45ceb6a6c55c3db8a","tid":1200499,"uid":215634,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ceaad5af8324ca3b10ae062283a12e0377321258","tid":1200499,"uid":215634,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:43:21.000Z","msg":"多得大家一齊諗偈，呢招好似真係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:44:30.000Z","msg":"work"},{"pid":"c94fdabe9cd71ce86aea5c9a80e9b3ba666cd4d1","tid":1200499,"uid":258381,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:01:56.000Z","msg":"一開始講得唔咁詳細可能會有巴打唔太明<br />\n<br />\nMPF既基金係Open-end<br />\n即係如果你賣左d基金單位，佢就會賣基金入面既資產，拎錢比返人<br />\n相反，你買基金個時，佢就會拎你d錢買多d資產<br />\n<br />\n所以由香港基金轉外國既原理就係<br />\n1. 你賣香港基金 &rarr; 基金公司賣香港資產（e.g. 港股） &rarr; 比返港幣你<br />\n2. 你再要港幣買外國基金（e.g. 美股） &rarr; 基金公司用港幣兌美元 &rarr; 買美股<br />\n<br />\n最後2個影響<br />\n1. 大量資金流出港股 &rarr; 港股跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 大量資金流出香港 &rarr; 港匯跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b843a69114d0d008d73ad29782753a07678a03c","tid":1200499,"uid":215634,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:03:54.000Z","msg":"孝子們，家中兩老強積金多年來無管理過，係時候展現孝心，幫手打理一下"},{"pid":"88228591c1035ef7025f2729da508490175a91f6","tid":1200499,"uid":215634,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:11:19.000Z","msg":"聽講公務員公積金政府會供多啲，仲唔快啲share俾你既公務員朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公務員一樣可以出一分力"},{"pid":"fff13ad008aa4af0b28c06216f0520bc0509f2a7","tid":1200499,"uid":95624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:21:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc6b5fd39caf0d2073ca46f7219c31eea7f12034","tid":1200499,"uid":175316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:24:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5db83078069694a65a0e4645737eb9f9eada2cd3","tid":1200499,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:52:39.000Z","msg":"mpf咁少錢，用一半身家沽股市期貨好過<br />\n不過唔想打銀彈，怕冇左啲錢嘅就算，明白錢對香港人嚟講最緊要<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pentoy.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E4%B8%81%E8%9F%B9-800x445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pentoy.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F%25E4%25B8%2581%25E8%259F%25B9-800x445.jpg&h=c509c42c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b744ac23bbe920224e67fc9a840661862443db9","tid":1200499,"uid":33618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5db83078069694a65a0e4645737eb9f9eada2cd3","tid":1200499,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:52:39.000Z","msg":"mpf咁少錢，用一半身家沽股市期貨好過<br />\n不過唔想打銀彈，怕冇左啲錢嘅就算，明白錢對香港人嚟講最緊要<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pentoy.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E4%B8%81%E8%9F%B9-800x445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht